<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Waste to Worth Farms</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbo-track': 'reload' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbo-track': 'reload' %>
  <style>
    /* General Styling */
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f9f9f9; /* Light gray background */
      color: #333;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
      color: #2c3e50; /* Dark gray */
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
  /* Hero Section */
.hero {
    background-color: #2c3e50;
    color: #fff; /* This already sets the text color to white */
    padding: 100px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: white; /* Ensures the h1 text is white */
}

.hero p {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: white; /* Ensures the paragraph text is white */
}


    .cta-button {
      padding: 10px 25px;
      background-color: #3CB371; /* Red */
      color: white;
      font-size: 18px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #ffffff; /* Darker red */
    }

    /* Features Section */
    .features {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      background-color: #ecf0f1; /* Light gray */
    }

    .feature {
      max-width: 300px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .feature h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .feature p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Join Us Section */
    .join-us {
      background-color: #ffffff; /* White background */
      color: #27ae60; /* Text color to match the theme */
      padding: 80px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .join-us h2 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cta-text {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .join-us p {
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    /* Testimonials Section */
    .testimonials {
      background-color: #ecf0f1; /* Light gray */
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .testimonials blockquote {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-style: italic;
      margin: 20px auto;
      max-width: 600px;
      color: #2c3e50; /* Dark gray */
    }

    /* Call to Action Section */
    .cta-secondary {
      padding: 50px 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff; /* White background */
      text-align: center;
      color: #f39c12; /* Text color to match the theme */
    }

    .cta-secondary h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .cta-secondary p {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark gray */
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    footer p, footer ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style-type: none;
    }

    footer ul li {
      display: inline;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #ecf0f1; /* Light gray for links */
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Turning Waste Into Worth</h1>
    <p>Join us in converting food waste from stores into valuable resources for sustainable farming.</p>
    <%= link_to "Learn More", about_path, class: "cta-button" %>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature">
      <h2>Biowaste to Feed</h2>
      <p>We collect surplus food and process it into nutritious animal feed, reducing waste and supporting local farms.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h2>Compost Creation</h2>
      <p>Our program transforms organic waste into rich compost that nourishes the soil and promotes sustainable agriculture.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h2>Natural Fertilizer</h2>
      <p>By recycling food waste, we produce eco-friendly fertilizers that help farmers grow healthier, more resilient crops.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Join Us Section -->
  <section class="join-us">
    <h2>Join Us in the Fight Against Food Waste</h2>
    <p>ProduceBridge is more than just a platform; it’s a movement toward a more sustainable and equitable food system. By joining our community, you’re playing a vital role in the fight against food waste and food insecurity.</p>
    <p class="cta-text">Get Started Today!</p>
    <p>Ready to make a difference? Sign up for free today and help us bridge the gap between surplus and need. Together, we can create a world where everyone has access to nutritious food, and where waste is a thing of the past.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials Section -->
  <section class="testimonials">
    <blockquote>
      "Waste to Worth Farms has been a game-changer for our farm. We’re getting affordable, high-quality feed, and reducing landfill waste at the same time." - Farmer Joe
    </blockquote>
    <blockquote>
      "It’s amazing to see food waste from our store being transformed into valuable resources. This initiative is a win-win for everyone!" - Store Manager Sarah
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <!-- Call-to-Action Section -->
  <section class="cta-secondary">
    <h2>Ready to make an impact?</h2>
    <p>Get involved today and help us create a greener, more sustainable future.</p>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Waste to Worth Farms. All rights reserved.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_path %></li>
      <li><%= link_to "Terms of Service", terms_path %></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Follow us on:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><%= link_to "Facebook", "https://facebook.com", target: "_blank" %></li>
      <li><%= link_to "Instagram", "https://instagram.com", target: "_blank" %></li>
      <li><%= link_to "Twitter", "https://twitter.com", target: "_blank" %></li>
    </ul>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
